ts and clip sizes etc.It maybe starts slow and you need to get used to the crafting and research mechanics, but im sure after 4-5 hours you feel right at home :)But take notice Win Xp is NOT supported !Mac and linux arent supported yet, but get a future implementation!Just check out the forums to get a better picture whats going on.When starting the game first time i strongly recommend doing the tutorial first.Edit2: Not recommended anymore, because its abandoneware. The website shut down and community manager got fired!"
